                 int yCenter,
                 gpdraw.SketchPad paper,
                 double ACChance,
                 boolean IsSnowing,
                 P1_Wang_Jake_FinalHouse house)
        Draws a singular apartment unit exterior
        Parameters:
        xCenter - : x value of the center of block, width is 200 px.
        yCenter - : y value of the center of block, height is 150 px.
        paper - : the SketchPad object to draw on (imported from gpdraw library).
        ACChance - : the probability that an air conditioning unit will be drawn on each apartment unit.
        IsSnowing - : whether or not to draw the unit with snow
        house - : FinalHouse object to call DrawAC with (now deprecated)
